{"tid":911922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【5死18傷】司機證實為村官之子 直撞學生涉酒駕毒駕","createTime":"2018-11-22T09:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T12:06:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c89208b79413eacc03022d60fade61fe3b2df6cd","tid":911922,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542871444_cac6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542871444_cac6.jpg&h=0cb54bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">奧迪撞飛學生後不顧而去，司機被捕時被拍到清楚面容。(互聯網)</span><br />\n<br />\n遼寧省葫蘆島市今日中午一部奧迪（Audi）A6房車在一間小學門前超速失控，撞向正在過馬路的小學生及教師，事故最少造成5死18傷，司機之後被警方迫停拘捕。涉事司機是當地一名村黨支部書記（村支書）的兒子，有網民則指事發時他不但超速、逆線行駛，更涉及醉酒、吸毒後駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者稱奧迪房車撞到學生之後不顧而去，繼續向市郊方向行駛，警車從後追截，將車逼到一處路邊的溝渠將車逼停，多名警員將司機制服，並且清楚拍下司機的容貌。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體證實，涉事司機是葫蘆島市建昌縣老達杖子鄉青牛山村村支書之子韓繼華，他是涉事車輛的登記車主，他名下獨自經營「建昌縣青牛山度假山莊」。他的父親表示目前人在外地，知道兒子闖出大禍，雖然內地工商信用系統顯示兒子的公司仍在經營，但韓父則稱「公司已經不開了」。<br />\n<br />\n「喪心病狂！」不少網民看過涉事的影片，都大罵事件如同「恐怖襲擊」，有網民質疑司機是「突然加速直接撞上去的」，稱這名司機真的是「瘋了」，稱「不管怎麼判，希望他不要再出來了」。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181122/58944342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58944342&d=%2FXlLKxHMo%2FigLamPEfJo7IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e6ee6c51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58944342&h=da1be560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181122/58944342</a>"},{"pid":"dfc8b6aa7e0952b07095af79514f1cdb565caa5b","tid":911922,"uid":184581,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"我爸是李剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888cb8f3d18340c592a48f925d649d90408ae32f","tid":911922,"uid":49643,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"做官咁細應該保唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795db5971e614177c33be3f9fbce6fad6a7e69f7","tid":911922,"uid":92640,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"葫蘆島市建昌縣老達杖子鄉青牛山村村支書之子"},{"pid":"3118144f383b8460df9223a9a4b5649d85b9cee0","tid":911922,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒 請不要造謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07132d7c0edd74e59c7f5d37f8bd84a230b0f9f4","tid":911922,"uid":96486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"做村官都咁多油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630c507c61360da07aa18caa941130b0c29d9d4e","tid":911922,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"有錢咪入去嘆幾個月世界.件事淡咗就話行為好放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3152ddd7fd48229c6bebed0d9c874d6425eba2da","tid":911922,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"係咪撞到啲人太出名呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9928cf7d9010ab8a9e20af4551e6355c5be292","tid":911922,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3152ddd7fd48229c6bebed0d9c874d6425eba2da","tid":911922,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"係咪撞到啲人太出名呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"暴龍哥都保佢唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879c5daeba20def6428be7c277d380733c30f0c4","tid":911922,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c